FastMultiset
public interface Multiset<E>
extends java.util.List<java.util.List<E>>

A representation of a set of elements where the like elements have been grouped. Usually, a multiset would just contain information about the quantities of the distinct types in a collection, but this implementation also holds the actual elements.

Author:
Christian Trimble
